                                "byte_start": 100552,
                                "byte_stop": 163559,
                                "text": "The judgments and opinion of the Court in 75-1126, Trans World Airlines against Hardison and the related case will be announced by Mr. Justice White."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 15.745,
                        "stop": 84.28,
